Package: pafr
Title: Read, manipulate and visualize 'Pairwise mApping Format' data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("David", "Winter", 
                  email = "david.winter@gmail.com", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"), 
                  comment  = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6165-0029")
           )
Description: Provides functions to read pairwise sequence alignments in the 'PAF' format used by 'minimap2' and 'miniasm'. 
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4.4),
    ggplot2,
Imports:
    dplyr, 
    tibble
